column5: Her 3rd birthday!!!! My daughter caught her first fish!!!! A 12" walleye to boot. Proud daddy
Great!!! Put 3 candles on it and have it for supper!
Loving the matching sweaters! Congrat's to your daughter, bigger than my PB eye!
very sweet lots to that story. heritage. keeping the future of the sport. and the best. family time. congrats
Great shots.  What a clan ya got there man!  HBD to the little angler kiddo!
good on ya ...moments frozen in time for eternity...HBD to the wee one
Awesome Rick….she's a real cute kid.  Say hi to that Pro guy for me eh?
Ill tell harv you called him an amateur lol. Hell call you shortly after lol

thanks simon! Will do! He was just asking me yesterday if your brave enough to come down lol   Its been a long time….your kid had no teeth the last visit.  If you guys supply the boat…i'll bring the bait!
That is totally awesome thanks for sharing with us
nice pictures, never been there but your neck of the woods looks like great place to be
